Package model.logic

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Replayable
    This interface is implemented by the classes that can be replayed in a Replay
    Reportable
    This interface is implemented by serializable Objects
    Rival
    This interface is an abstraction of the participants in a Rolit game: players, teams, etc.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    This class represents the physical Board of a Rolit game
    Cube
    This class represents a cube tile from the Rolit game
    Game
    This class represents a Rolit Game and is in charge of managing each player turn.
    GameClassic
    This class represents the Classic game mode of Rolit.
    GameTeams
    This class represents the Team game mode of Rolit.
    Player
    This class represents a Rolit player
    Team
    This class represents a team form GameTeams mode
    TurnManager
    This class is in charge of managing who is the next Player and make it play
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Color
    This enum class represents each player color
    Shape
    This class represents the shape of a Board
